@{
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/Effect.cshtml";
}

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Student Management System</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .features {
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-left: 40px;
        }

            .features ul {
                list-style: none;
                padding: 0;
            }

            .features li {
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                font-size: 16px;
                line-height: 1.6;
            }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

            .btn-primary:hover {
                background-color: #0056b3;
            }

        .cta-section {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 0;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

            .cta-section h3 {
                font-size: 30px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .cta-section p {
                font-size: 18px;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

        .cta-btn {
            background-color: #e74c3c;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-size: 20px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

            .cta-btn:hover {
                background-color: #c0392b;
            }

        .features img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to the Student Management System</h1>
        <p>
            Our Student Management System (SMS) simplifies administrative tasks, improves student engagement, and increases operational efficiency. From student records to academic performance, our platform is designed to help educational institutions streamline their processes.
        </p>

        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <div class="features">
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Student Profiles:</strong> Maintain comprehensive student records, including personal details, academic history, contact information, and more.</li>
                <li><strong>Attendance Tracking:</strong> Effortlessly track attendance with real-time updates, and generate detailed attendance reports.</li>
                <li><strong>Grading System:</strong> Simplify grading, track progress, and automatically calculate student scores for each course.</li>
                <li><strong>Course Management:</strong> Create and manage courses, assignments, and exams, while scheduling them efficiently.</li>
                <li><strong>Notifications & Announcements:</strong> Instantly send real-time notifications to students and staff regarding important events, exams, and updates.</li>
                <li><strong>Data Analytics:</strong> Access insightful reports and data on student performance, attendance, and other critical metrics.</li>
                <li><strong>Secure Access:</strong> Role-based access control to ensure that only authorized users can access sensitive data.</li>
            </ul>
            
        </div>

        <div class="cta-section">
            <h3>Transform the way you manage students</h3>
            <p>Our comprehensive student management solution is here to enhance the learning experience, reduce manual tasks, and bring innovation to your institution.</p>
            <a href="#" class="cta-btn">Get Started Now</a>
        </div>

        <p>Our mission is to simplify the way educational institutions operate by leveraging technology to foster growth, productivity, and operational excellence. Whether you're a school, college, or university, we have the tools to help you succeed.</p>

        <p><strong>Empower your institution with our student management solution today!</strong></p>

        <a href="#features" class="btn-primary">Learn More About Features</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
